@@TJvInstaller.InstallAsShared@string
Description:
Use this method to install a file as a shared file. This way, the file will be registered in the system as it, and won't be deleted until you have uninstalled your program (until you have explicitely removed your file from the shared list). This solution is the best for shared libraries (dll, ocx, ...)

